sect1.para:
It may bring some comfort to organizations experiencing employee bullying within the workplace that the problem of bullying is international. Germany reports having 17% of their workforce report bullying. In the United States, 30% of the workforce report having experienced bullying; 30% translates to an estimation of 48.6 million working adults. India has an estimated 46% to 55% of workplace bullying (Praslova et al., 
               2022
            ).
